snippet.textDisplay: This song is so beautiful and unique. The moment the music transitions from Hanan's part to Kaasvish's part at around 3:06 a kind of amnesia hits your brain and you totally forget about the first part of the song. And that transition at around 3:06, merges the two parts so beautifully and subtly. It almost feels like a new soul enters your body and it gives a very subtle shock to your brain and then it all melts inside. I am not sure how to describe this feeling but a great job done by coke studio.
